Relaxometry With TESS
As proposed for rapid quantification of T2 from double echo steady state (DESS) (9), we follow the initial idea of exploiting the dependencies of the modes on relaxation to quantify T1 and T2. To this end, we investigate the following signal ratios (see Fig. 2):

